<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>About Us - HomeBitez</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:wght@600;700;800&family=Manrope:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
  :root{
    --cream:#faefe5;
    --card:#fff7ee;
    --ink:#2a241e;
    --muted:#6f6256;
    --accent:#d59b2d;
    --accent-deep:#b97d18;
    --line:#eadac6;
  }

  body{
    margin:0;
    font-family: "Manrope", "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
    background:
      radial-gradient(900px 500px at 10% -10%, #fff1de 0%, transparent 60%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, var(--cream) 0%, #fff8f0 100%);
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .wrap{
    max-width: 1120px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 40px 20px 70px;
  }

  .hero{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    gap: 26px;
    align-items: center;
    background: #fffdf8;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 22px;
    padding: 28px;
    box-shadow: 0 14px 34px rgba(42,36,30,0.10);
  }

  .title{
    font-family: "Fraunces", "Times New Roman", serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 38px;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .subtitle{
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  .cta-row{
    display:flex;
    gap:12px;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
  }

  .btn-menu{
    padding: 12px 22px;
    background: var(--accent);
    color:white;
    border-radius:999px;
    border:none;
    font-weight:700;
    text-decoration:none;
    display:inline-flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:center;
  }
  .btn-menu:hover{ background: var(--accent-deep); }

  .btn-ghost{
    padding: 12px 22px;
    border-radius:999px;
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration:none;
    font-weight:700;
    background:#fff;
  }

  .photo-stack{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .photo{
    height: 150px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, #ffe7c4, #fff6e5);
    background-image:
      var(--img),
      linear-gradient(135deg, #ffe7c4, #fff6e5);
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
  }
  .photo.tall{ height: 220px; grid-column: span 2; }

  .sections{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 18px;
    margin-top: 26px;
  }

  .card{
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 18px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(42,36,30,0.08);
  }

  .card h5{
    font-family: "Fraunces", "Times New Roman", serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .chip{
    display:inline-block;
    padding: 6px 10px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #fff7ea;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
    font-size: 12px;
    margin: 6px 8px 0 0;
  }

  .list{
    margin:0;
    padding-left:18px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .footer-row{
    margin-top: 26px;
    display:flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px){
    .hero{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .sections{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="wrap">
  <div class="hero">
    <div>
      <div class="title">About HomeBitez</div>
      <p class="subtitle">
        HomeBitez is built to make ordering simple, fast, and fuss free so you can get your favorite meals with less waiting and more convenience.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-row">
        <a href="/login" class="btn-menu">Browse Menu</a>
        <a href="/" class="btn-ghost">Back to Home</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="photo-stack">
      <div class="photo" style="--img:url('/images/about-3.jpg');"></div>
      <div class="photo" style="--img:url('/images/about-2.jpg');"></div>
      <div class="photo tall" style="--img:url('/images/about-1.jpg');"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="sections">
    <div class="card">
      <h5>Our Mission</h5>
      <p>
        To provide an easy, friendly food ordering experience with clear menu info, smooth checkout, and reliable pickup.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h5>What We Offer</h5>
      <div class="chip">Browse menu by categories</div>
      <div class="chip">Add to cart instantly</div>
      <div class="chip">Edit cart quantities easily</div>
      <div class="chip">Cutlery toggle</div>
      <div class="chip">Pickup date and time selection</div>
      <div class="chip">Smooth checkout flow</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h5>Why HomeBitez?</h5>
      <ul class="list">
        <li>Simple interface that is easy to use</li>
        <li>Clear prices and quick cart management</li>
        <li>Designed to be clean, modern, and mobile friendly</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer-row">
    <div class="subtitle" style="margin:0;">
      Built with care for busy days and hungry nights.
    </div>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn-ghost">Contact Us</a>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
